HOW CAN PERIPHERAL BODILY 
EVENTS INFLUENCE EMOTIONS?
• hold pencil tightly between teeth 
(forces smiling expression) or between 
lips (prevents smiling) while watching 
funny movie - smiling expression led to 
more enjoyment
• pose facial muscles (into smile or 
frown) - see pictures - then report 
feelings - frown expression reported 
more anger and less happiness

